raising and all that stuff

00:31:22.590 --> 00:31:26.360
and also wanting to keep tabs
on them through the year.

00:31:26.360 --> 00:31:28.120
Because I always
find, even as adults,

00:31:28.120 --> 00:31:30.280
when we're involved in
a really amazing project

00:31:30.280 --> 00:31:33.100
