these girls, who

00:31:34.760 --> 00:31:36.950
have these kind of shitty
home life, a lot of them.

00:31:36.950 --> 00:31:40.520
And they go from this magical
10 days, and then they go back.

00:31:40.520 --> 00:31:44.010
