they felt like it wasn't over.

00:31:44.010 --> 00:31:47.430
And through the year,
we do little reunions.

00:31:47.430 --> 00:31:49.710
And they go see shows
together, and we

00:31:49.710 --> 00:31:53.590
go see art and tap dance.

00:31:53.590 --> 00:31:56.370
We have like dance
things and whatever.

00:31:56.370 --> 00:32:01.316
Anyway, so it's a constantly
evolving foundation.

00:32:01.316 --> 00:32:02.690
We want to get to
the point where

00:32:02.690 --> 00:32:05.450
